SW_CORE   -->  VLAN_SRV  : Access port VLAN 20
SW_CORE   -->  VLAN_MGT  : Access port VLAN 30
SW_CORE   -->  ACL_INT

' ComunicaciГіn SGISI в†’ MySQL (la conexiГіn central del sistema)
